Enum Summary
BackupManager.BackupType The backup type specified the directory from whic or to which the backup manager is backuping/restoring.
Context.ContextLabel The context label describes through which component the context was created (i.e., the prior "where" field).
Context.ContextState Context state, used for editorial workflows
Context.ContextType Context types: USER -> data written by user (e.g. wiki, edit form) CLI -> data loaded via CLI SYSTEM -> data created automatically by the system PROVIDER -> data provider COMMUNICATIONSERVICE -> communication service METACONTEXT -> the one and only meta context (fixed URI)
